  "detailed_description": "<strong>FIGHT EVIL SPIRITS FOR THE GOOD OF THE KINGDOM!</strong><br>Interesting locations, which are assembled by hand, are waiting for heroes who can save the fading kingdom from hordes of evil spirits! The brave king longs for salvation for all his subjects, which is why he calls the HEROES on an adventure that can end tragically...<br><br><strong>COLLECT UNIQUE BUILDS</strong><br>There are many ways to become stronger in the game, and a lot of items will help in this. Destroy monsters and raise your level, as well as collect gold, which can be spent on the development of your hero.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"{STEAM_APP_IMAGE}/extras/Видео_без_названия_—_сделано_в_Clipchamp.gif/img]\n\n[b]EXPLORE WORLDS AND DEFEAT EVIL[/b]\nThe world is full of dangers, every region is under the custody of great monsters... Search for boss portals and summon them to save the kingdom!\n\n[imgvid poster.avif=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2774560/extras/bcb5a34390a2d6a4b99eed48bd461052.poster.avif?t=1716457932\" webm=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2774560/extras/bcb5a34390a2d6a4b99eed48bd461052.webm?t=1716457932\" mp4=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2774560/extras/bcb5a34390a2d6a4b99eed48bd461052.mp4?t=1716457932\" width=\"426\" height=\"240\"]\" crossorigin=\"anonymous\" /></span><br><br><strong>EXPLORE WORLDS AND DEFEAT EVIL</strong><br>The world is full of dangers, every region is under the custody of great monsters... Search for boss portals and summon them to save the kingdom!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2774560/extras/bcb5a34390a2d6a4b99eed48bd461052.poster.avif?t=1716457932\" width=426 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2774560/extras/bcb5a34390a2d6a4b99eed48bd461052.webm?t=1716457932\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2774560/extras/bcb5a34390a2d6a4b99eed48bd461052.mp4?t=1716457932\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
  "about_the_game": "<strong>FIGHT EVIL SPIRITS FOR THE GOOD OF THE KINGDOM!</strong><br>Interesting locations, which are assembled by hand, are waiting for heroes who can save the fading kingdom from hordes of evil spirits! The brave king longs for salvation for all his subjects, which is why he calls the HEROES on an adventure that can end tragically...<br><br><strong>COLLECT UNIQUE BUILDS</strong><br>There are many ways to become stronger in the game, and a lot of items will help in this. Destroy monsters and raise your level, as well as collect gold, which can be spent on the development of your hero.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"{STEAM_APP_IMAGE}/extras/Видео_без_названия_—_сделано_в_Clipchamp.gif/img]\n\n[b]EXPLORE WORLDS AND DEFEAT EVIL[/b]\nThe world is full of dangers, every region is under the custody of great monsters... Search for boss portals and summon them to save the kingdom!\n\n[imgvid poster.avif=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2774560/extras/bcb5a34390a2d6a4b99eed48bd461052.poster.avif?t=1716457932\" webm=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2774560/extras/bcb5a34390a2d6a4b99eed48bd461052.webm?t=1716457932\" mp4=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2774560/extras/bcb5a34390a2d6a4b99eed48bd461052.mp4?t=1716457932\" width=\"426\" height=\"240\"]\" crossorigin=\"anonymous\" /></span><br><br><strong>EXPLORE WORLDS AND DEFEAT EVIL</strong><br>The world is full of dangers, every region is under the custody of great monsters... Search for boss portals and summon them to save the kingdom!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2774560/extras/bcb5a34390a2d6a4b99eed48bd461052.poster.avif?t=1716457932\" width=426 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/ap